// UnifiedEditor
// Central routing component that picks the correct editor for a session item
// based on its type: design, spreadsheet, snippet group, or diagram/document.
// For diagram/document items it also renders the preview pane and handles
// version history preview mode.

FUNCTION SnippetGroupView(groupId, snippets, ...) -> JSX
  CALLS: SnippetEditor (SnippetEditor)
  Finds all snippets sharing the same groupId.
  Renders a tab bar listing each snippet in the group by file path.
  Delegates to SnippetEditor for the active tab.

---

FUNCTION handleSnippetSave(snippet) -> void
  Bridges the SnippetEditor onSave callback to the parent onSnippetSave prop.

---

FUNCTION getDiffContents() -> {before, after}
  Reads historyDiff.compareMode from the store.
  IF vs-current: returns {before: historicalContent, after: currentContent}.
  IF vs-previous: returns {before: previousHistoricalContent, after: historicalContent}.

---

FUNCTION previewComponent() -> JSX
  CALLS: MermaidPreview (MermaidPreview), MarkdownPreview (MarkdownPreview)
  IF diagram and historyDiff active: returns DiffView (side-by-side mermaid).
  IF diagram: returns MermaidPreview.
  IF document and historyDiff active: returns MarkdownPreview with inline diff.
  IF document: returns MarkdownPreview.

---

FUNCTION handleFormat() -> void
  Calls formatMermaid on the current diagram content.
  IF successful, calls onContentChange with the formatted string.

---

FUNCTION UnifiedEditor(item, ...) -> JSX                               EXPORT
  CALLS: DesignEditor (DesignEditor), SpreadsheetEditor (SpreadsheetEditor),
         DiagramEditor (DiagramEditor), DocumentEditor (DocumentEditor)
  Routes by item.type:
    design -> DesignEditor
    spreadsheet -> SpreadsheetEditor
    snippet -> SnippetGroupView (groups by groupId)
    diagram / document -> SplitPane with CodeMirrorWrapper + previewComponent
  IF diagram history preview mode: renders DiagramHistoryPreview instead of
  the normal editor.
